ances to ensure client data is secure.</li><li>We clear funds through the Federal Reserve, removing the risk of insufficient funds or chargebacks.</li><li>Accruit undergoes rigorous third-party compliance assessments of our people, processes, and technologies annually.</li><li>Our employees undergo pre-employment background checks and participate in ongoing trainings related to safety, security, risk-management, protection of non-public private information (NPI), fraud prevention and ethics.</li><li>Accruit partners with Fortune 50 cloud providers to support, maintain, and protect our data, networks, and infrastructure from all types of cyber hacking and security threats. In the unlikely event of a service disruption, we maintain a comprehensive business continuity and disaster recovery policy, which is regularly tested.</li></ul><h3></h3><h3 style="text-align: left;">Interested in partnering with us?</h3><p style="text-align: left;">Our partners include auction houses, online auctions, classified magazines and other trade organizations. If you would like to learn more about how our KingsTrust<sup style="font-size: 9px;">®</sup> service can provide financial protection for you and your customers, please contact us at support@kingstrustescrow.com.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section  class="wpb_row main_row  row-line-seperator" style="text-align:center; background-color:#eeeeef; color:#ffffff; padding-top:50px; padding-bottom:30px;"><div class="row-inner"><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12 vc_col-lg-offset-0 vc_col-md-offset-0 vc_col-sm-offset-0"><div class="vc_column-inner "><div class="wpb_wrapper"><div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " ><div class="wpb_wrapper"><h3 style="text-align: center; color: #333;">Ready to give KingsTrust<sup style="font-size: 9px;">®</sup> a try? Get started today!</h3></div></div><div class="vc_empty_space"   style="height: 25px" ><span class="vc_empty_space_in